<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>MeuNutri – Seu Plano de Emagrecimento</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;700&display=swap');

  :root {
    --bg: #0f1117;
    --surface: #1a1d27;
    --surface2: #22263a;
    --accent: #4ade80;
    --accent2: #22d3ee;
    --warn: #fb923c;
    --danger: #f87171;
    --text: #f0f4ff;
    --muted: #8892b0;
    --border: #2e3455;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 12px 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
  }
  .logo {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }
  .logo span { color: var(--text); }
  .nav-date { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); }

  /* TABS */
  .tabs {
    display: flex;
    background: var(--surface);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    overflow-x: auto;
    scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  .tab-btn {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 90px;
    padding: 12px 8px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    cursor: pointer;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .tab-btn.active {
    color: var(--accent);
    border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
  }
  .tab-icon { display: block; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2px; }

  /* SECTIONS */
  .section { display: none; padding: 16px; }
  .section.active { display: block; }

  /* CARDS */
  .card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .card-title {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  /* MACRO RING */
  .macro-summary {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .ring-wrap { position: relative; width: 100px; height: 100px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .ring-wrap svg { transform: rotate(-90deg); }
  .ring-center {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .ring-kcal { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); line-height: 1; }
  .ring-label { font-size: 0.62rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; }
  .macro-list { flex: 1; }
  .macro-item { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .macro-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.78rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .macro-name { color: var(--muted); }
  .macro-val { font-weight: 600; }
  .bar { height: 5px; background: var(--surface2); border-radius: 99px; overflow: hidden; }
  .bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 99px; transition: width 0.6s ease; }

  /* MEALS */
  .meal-block { margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .meal-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .meal-title-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .meal-icon { font-size: 1.2rem; }
  .meal-name { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; }
  .meal-company-badge {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    background: #1e3a2f;
    color: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 2px 7px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .meal-kcal { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); }
  .meal-add-btn {
    background: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--muted);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .meal-add-btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
  .food-list { padding: 8px 0; }
  .food-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 7px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1e2235;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
  }
  .food-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .food-name { color: var(--text); flex: 1; }
  .food-qty { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.75rem; margin: 0 10px; }
  .food-cal { color: var(--accent2); font-weight: 600; min-width: 55px; text-align: right; }
  .food-del {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: #444;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    padding: 2px 5px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .food-del:hover { color: var(--danger); }

  /* MODAL */
  .modal-overlay {
    display: none;
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    z-index: 999;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .modal-overlay.open { display: flex; }
  .modal {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0;
    padding: 20px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 480px;
    max-height: 80vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
    animation: slideUp 0.3s ease;
  }
  @keyframes slideUp {
    from { transform: translateY(100%); opacity: 0; }
    to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
  }
  .modal-title {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .modal-close {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: none;
    color: var(--muted);
    border-radius: 50%;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .search-input {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    outline: none;
  }
  .search-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .food-option {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .food-option:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .food-option-name { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500; }
  .food-option-info { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; }
  .food-option-cal { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }
  .qty-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin: 12px 0;
  }
  .qty-row label { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); white-space: nowrap; }
  .qty-input {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    outline: none;
  }
  .qty-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .add-confirm-btn {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #0f1117;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 13px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .add-confirm-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

  /* JANTA SUGESTÕES */
  .janta-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .janta-card {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 12px;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .janta-card:hover, .janta-card.selected { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .janta-card.selected { background: #1a2e21; }
  .janta-emoji { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .janta-name { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.2; }
  .janta-cal { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--accent); margin-top: 4px; }
  .janta-macros { font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; }
  .use-janta-btn {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--accent2);
    color: #0f1117;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 11px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .use-janta-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
  .use-janta-btn:disabled { opacity: 0.4; cursor: not-allowed; }

  /* PROGRESSO */
  .progress-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .progress-big { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; line-height: 1; }
  .progress-sub { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 4px; }
  .progress-target { text-align: right; }
  .progress-target-num { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--muted); }
  .progress-target-label { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--muted); }
  .weight-bar-wrap { margin: 6px 0 16px; }
  .weight-label-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .weight-bar { height: 8px; background: var(--surface2); border-radius: 99px; overflow: hidden; }
  .weight-bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 99px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2)); transition: width 0.8s ease; }

  .weight-input-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .weight-input {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    outline: none;
  }
  .weight-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .weight-save-btn {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #0f1117;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }

  /* HISTORICO DE PESO */
  .weight-history { margin-top: 14px; }
  .weight-entry {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
  }
  .weight-entry:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .weight-entry-date { color: var(--muted); }
  .weight-entry-val { font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
  .weight-delta-pos { color: var(--danger); font-size: 0.75rem; }
  .weight-delta-neg { color: var(--accent); font-size: 0.75rem; }

  /* DICAS */
  .tip-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2e1a, #1e2e3a);
    border: 1px solid #2a4a2a;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .tip-header { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .tip-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; }
  .tip-title { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .tip-body { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* TOAST */
  .toast {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 20px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(20px);
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #0f1117;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 30px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    z-index: 9999;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .toast.show {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
  }

  /* STATS ROW */
  .stats-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .stat-box {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 12px 8px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat-val { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 800; }
  .stat-unit { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--muted); }

  /* SEMANA */
  .week-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .day-dot {
    flex: 1;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 6px 0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .day-dot.today { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }
  .day-dot.done { background: #1a2e21; border-color: var(--accent); }
  .day-dot-label { font-size: 0.6rem; color: var(--muted); display: block; }
  .day-dot-pct { font-size: 0.65rem; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="logo">Meu<span>Nutri</span></div>
  <div class="nav-date" id="navDate"></div>
</nav>

<div class="tabs">
  <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="showTab('hoje')">
    <span class="tab-icon">🍽️</span>Hoje
  </button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('janta')">
    <span class="tab-icon">🌙</span>Jantar
  </button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('progresso')">
    <span class="tab-icon">📊</span>Progresso
  </button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('dicas')">
    <span class="tab-icon">💡</span>Dicas
  </button>
</div>

<!-- ===== ABA HOJE ===== -->
<div class="section active" id="tab-hoje">

  <!-- Semana -->
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">Semana atual</div>
    <div class="week-row" id="weekRow"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Macros -->
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">Calorias & Macros hoje</div>
    <div class="macro-summary">
      <div class="ring-wrap">
        <svg width="100" height="100" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
          <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="40" fill="none" stroke="#22263a" stroke-width="10"/>
          <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="40" fill="none" stroke="#4ade80" stroke-width="10"
            stroke-dasharray="251.2" stroke-dashoffset="251.2"
            id="calRing" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="ring-center">
          <div class="ring-kcal" id="calEaten">0</div>
          <div class="ring-label">kcal</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="macro-list">
        <div class="macro-item">
          <div class="macro-row">
            <span class="macro-name">Proteína</span>
            <span class="macro-val" id="prot-val">0 / 180g</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bar"><div class="bar-fill" id="prot-bar" style="width:0%;background:#4ade80"></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="macro-item">
          <div class="macro-row">
            <span class="macro-name">Carbo</span>
            <span class="macro-val" id="carb-val">0 / 270g</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bar"><div class="bar-fill" id="carb-bar" style="width:0%;background:#22d3ee"></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="macro-item">
          <div class="macro-row">
            <span class="macro-name">Gordura</span>
            <span class="macro-val" id="fat-val">0 / 67g</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bar"><div class="bar-fill" id="fat-bar" style="width:0%;background:#fb923c"></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="stats-row">
      <div class="stat-box">
        <div class="stat-val" style="color:var(--accent)" id="calLeft">2400</div>
        <div class="stat-unit">kcal restantes</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-box">
        <div class="stat-val" style="color:var(--accent2)">2400</div>
        <div class="stat-unit">kcal meta</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-box">
        <div class="stat-val" style="color:var(--warn)" id="calPct">0%</div>
        <div class="stat-unit">do objetivo</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Refeições -->
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">Refeições</div>

    <div class="meal-block">
      <div class="meal-header">
        <div class="meal-title-row">
          <span class="meal-icon">☕</span>
          <span class="meal-name">Café da manhã</span>
          <span class="meal-company-badge">Empresa</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center">
          <span class="meal-kcal" id="kcal-cafe">0 kcal</span>
          <button class="meal-add-btn" onclick="openModal('cafe')">+ add</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="food-list" id="list-cafe"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="meal-block">
      <div class="meal-header">
        <div class="meal-title-row">
          <span class="meal-icon">🍱</span>
          <span class="meal-name">Almoço</span>
          <span class="meal-company-badge">Empresa</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center">
          <span class="meal-kcal" id="kcal-almoco">0 kcal</span>
          <button class="meal-add-btn" onclick="openModal('almoco')">+ add</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="food-list" id="list-almoco"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="meal-block">
      <div class="meal-header">
        <div class="meal-title-row">
          <span class="meal-icon">🌙</span>
          <span class="meal-name">Jantar</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center">
          <span class="meal-kcal" id="kcal-jantar">0 kcal</span>
          <button class="meal-add-btn" onclick="showTab('janta');document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn')[1].classList.add('active')">sugestões</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="food-list" id="list-jantar"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="meal-block">
      <div class="meal-header">
        <div class="meal-title-row">
          <span class="meal-icon">🍎</span>
          <span class="meal-name">Lanche</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center">
          <span class="meal-kcal" id="kcal-lanche">0 kcal</span>
          <button class="meal-add-btn" onclick="openModal('lanche')">+ add</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="food-list" id="list-lanche"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ===== ABA JANTAR ===== -->
<div class="section" id="tab-janta">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">💡 Jantares rápidos – escolha o seu</div>
    <p style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:14px;">Opções simples de fazer em casa, dentro da sua meta calórica noturna.</p>
    <div class="janta-grid" id="jantaGrid"></div>
    <button class="use-janta-btn" id="useJantaBtn" disabled onclick="addJantaSelecionado()">Adicionar ao jantar de hoje</button>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">📋 Como preparar</div>
    <div id="jantaRecipe" style="font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;">
      Selecione um jantar acima para ver o modo de preparo.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ===== ABA PROGRESSO ===== -->
<div class="section" id="tab-progresso">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">🏆 Meta de emagrecimento</div>
    <div class="progress-header">
      <div>
        <div class="progress-big" id="pesoAtual">–</div>
        <div class="progress-sub">seu peso atual (kg)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="progress-target">
        <div class="progress-target-num">– kg perdidos</div>
        <div class="progress-target-label" id="perdidoLabel">meta: 30 kg até jan/2027</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="weight-bar-wrap">
      <div class="weight-label-row">
        <span id="pesoInicial">Peso inicial</span>
        <span>Meta: 30 kg perdidos</span>
      </div>
      <div class="weight-bar">
        <div class="weight-bar-fill" id="weightBarFill" style="width:0%"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="weight-input-row">
      <input type="number" class="weight-input" id="weightIn" placeholder="Registrar peso hoje (kg)" step="0.1">
      <button class="weight-save-btn" onclick="saveWeight()">Salvar</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
